{"tid":1193271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日小心俾泛民影相","createTime":"2019-06-08T22:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T05:17:57.000Z","uid":157994,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d386a2524d813a07bdec43e47bf5a90cee90528a","tid":1193271,"uid":157994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T22:59:59.000Z","msg":"帽<br />\n口罩 黑衫褲必備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e22e830b93ab464f85af90a97d35ab37ed7f539","tid":1193271,"uid":130406,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T23:00:57.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 有乜都留返遊行後攪 和理非請遊完返屋企<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1193255\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1193255</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2cff5cd6ae6da7f37ff2910112eae2d3d83b99e2","tid":1193271,"uid":27664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T23:12:20.000Z","msg":"泛民影相同警察隨身Cam 係一樣作用"},{"pid":"9ce8718b996fae1306525a13f50ec95b6b904367","tid":1193271,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T23:21:56.000Z","msg":"阻住佢地影相應該唔犯法掛，記得唔好企唔穩撞跌人地部機同埋踩爛個鏡頭，不過到時人多擠逼，好難避免<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d56a1b45cb6c3c842b3247e93f7bd4f7ebb1276","tid":1193271,"uid":148987,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T23:26:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">提防糾察散水篤灰</span>"},{"pid":"162b711b929f754f50fbcbc0761a6c295c365977","tid":1193271,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T23:50:23.000Z","msg":"-遊行起點：銅鑼灣維多利亞公園中央草坪 （維園草地）<br />\n-遊行路線：維園草地起點&gt;高士威道&gt; 禮頓道&gt;伊榮街&gt;邊寧頓街&gt;軒尼詩道西行車路&gt;金鐘道&gt;樂禮街&gt;夏愨道&gt;添美道&gt;立法會外行人路終點<br />\n-集合時間：2：30PM<br />\n-起步時間：3：00PM（或維園草地達八成滿）<br />\n-衝定唔衝，自己執生<br />\n-記得宗旨：不散<br />\n<br />\n溫和：<br />\n<strong>【長期置頂】69反送中遊行須知整合</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1191837/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1191837/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[懶人包] 第一次參加遊行的常見疑問Q&amp;A</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1186623/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1186623/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【極重要】69遊行記得帶防Rfid卡套</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1190797/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1190797/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n勇武： <br />\n<strong>食放題須知，全部資料，一世受用</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1191403/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1191403/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[law撚］被捕人仕須知</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1189300/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1189300/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>［抗爭手冊］End game前準備</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1169374/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1169374/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑色三毛警告信號現正生效 6月8日16時</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">表示連登 facebook 網絡廣泛地區已錄得或預料會有每秒三毛回覆量超過70次/禁70次正評的網絡分化攻勢，且攻勢可能持續或於今晚或明朝早上升級。</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNv7C24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNv7C24.jpg&h=73f7da13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">注意事項</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>網民應注意username 同 三毛開post 目的 而非三毛post正評數量。<br />\n網民應負皮三毛post 入去屌佢老母 而毋須參與分化討論。<br />\n鍵盤戰士應努力推正經post 例如準備時項去抵擋三毛攻勢。<br />\n三毛會開一啲反共post 減低大家戒心 請細心思考現時網絡上所有言論。<br />\n一般市民應少上連登 關電視 而休養等待明天遊行。<br />\n鬼得一隻 林奠 其他完全唔重要 。</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZB4gyv7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZB4gyv7.gif&h=7cacc0df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f273c8126a33e56ffd43c0dbbc6b4bc916a25376","tid":1193271,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d386a2524d813a07bdec43e47bf5a90cee90528a","tid":1193271,"uid":157994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T22:59:59.000Z","msg":"帽<br />\n口罩 黑衫褲必備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T01:22:18.000Z","msg":"我驚你中暑暈低先<br />\n<br />\n6月9號遊行嘅方針:兄弟爬山，各自努力，避免割席，拒絕篤灰，不打飛機，不傳耳語，不搞抹黑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1192414\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1192414</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9358293466ecdb6d5fee6691fb839a5f7de768cd","tid":1193271,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T01:23:21.000Z","msg":"勇武派調虎離山 打突擊仲好<br />\n<br />\n又唔使俾和平遊行人士阻住哂，<br />\n<br />\nd差佬又去哂遊行度<br />\n<br />\n根本就應該有策略地互相配合，而唔係互相衝突"},{"pid":"3766e8a1941d65410ce2b008cf9d43a770b16cbb","tid":1193271,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T04:56:52.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 有乜都留返遊行後攪 和理非請遊完返屋企<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1193255\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1193255</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b5df3658fa810c78b4c0f6269a8d41e819a4ebfa","tid":1193271,"uid":28397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T05:11:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.wikihow.com/Blind-a-Surveillance-Camera\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.wikihow.com%2FBlind-a-Surveillance-Camera&d=%2BD6XGwqev%2FlZKpArKwvoHbvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=5e976f84\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.wikihow.com/Blind-a-Surveillance-Camera</a>"},{"pid":"5f8930ec45cd449f7e4d72321d51880fa1ded439","tid":1193271,"uid":28397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T05:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.google.com/imgres?imgurl=https%3A%